-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                                                          DATA/COLLECTIONS
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The entire app is essentially based around tasks and teams, with users and messages providing the necessary scaffolding.

1. Tasks

i.   title
ii.  decription
iii. priority: red , green or blue
iv.  assigned by
v.   assigned to
vi.  status: complete,incomplete
vii. view access: secret, team access

2. Teams

i.   name
ii.  decription
iii. current objectives
iv.  leader
v.   members

3. Messages

i.   message
ii.  sent by
iii. sent to

4.Users

i.   name
ii.  username
iii. email
iv.  profile pic
v.   position in company
vi.  job decription
